{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#1791: @vue/server-renderer doesn't have support for component-level caching",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:28:20.396651+00:00",
  "text": "@vue/server-renderer doesn't have support for component-level caching\n\n### What problem does this feature solve?\r\nServerCacheKey is useful feature for large projects with SSR. Will it be added to @vue/server-renderer?\r\n\r\n### What does the proposed API look like?\r\nhttps://ssr.vuejs.org/guide/caching.html#component-level-caching\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    ":sparkles: feature request",
    "scope: ssr"
  ],
